Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:29.34,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,計算どおりだって　あなたは笑うのかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I wonder if you're laughing now about how{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}it all went according to your calculations.
