Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirimosezu uzumoreshi intoku no tane\NA seed of secrecy buried where no one knows
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.35,0:23:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Moroha no ken\NA double-edged sword
